dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents municipalities for Green Lake County, Wisconsin in 2012. Highways have a width from the centerline out each direction to a right-of-way line. Municipalities have legal written descriptions that may follow the centerline, or the right-of-way line. Municipalities may also have boundary lines that follow the centerline, or either bank of a body of water.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
